700965f-b.title: Bronx: Eastchester Road - Adee Avenue
700965f-b.text:
Eastchester Road, adjoining and at the S.E. corner of Adee Ave., showing the Eoly Rosary Roman Catholic Church and rectory. The
rectory bears No. 2950.
V25~35E7  June 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, as seen from the opposite direction, showing a comprehensive view of the rectory.
June 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
